column3: Description

Fun, Flirty and bold V-neck style dress. This dress has a roached waist and flirty chiffon skirt. The straps have fully beaded accenting to add a touch of glam. Comes in two colors (Sunshine and Pistachio)

This elegant red cocktail dress combines simplicity with striking sophistication. The deep V neckline adds a bold yet refined touch, while the structured bodice and flared A-line skirt create a flattering silhouette that moves gracefully. Made from high-quality satin fabric, the dress offers a subtle sheen, making it perfect for cocktail parties, date nights, or any special occasion where you want to make a lasting impression. The sleeveless design enhances its timeless appeal, ensuring versatility and effortless style.
Simple yet elegant strapless chiffon dress, complete with a geometrical waist line accent.
Simple yet elegant strapless taffeta dress, complete with a floral waist line accent.
Red cocktail dress with plunging neckline! Beautiful red and white encrusted gems sewn onto see-through mesh highlighting the waistline. Perfect for any special occasion.

Elegant halter style dress with side cutouts. The front of the bodice is encrusted with gems to give it that regal look. The front connects by mesh fabric to give a barely there illusion. This dress also has pockets trimmed with matching gems.
Strapless chiffon overlay dress with beaded bodice. The cut-outs expose a fully beaded peek-a-boo accent!
Sleeping beauty inspired dress with fully beaded bodice and zip enclosure
Strapless, Mermaid cocktail dress with black accenting

Strapless sweetheart neckline with ruched pattern bodice accented with a center flower detail embroidery and comes with a mid thigh level skirt. This captivating dress combines modern elegance with intricate detailing, perfect for any upscale event. The deep space blue lace overlay is adorned with delicate beading, creating a sparkling effect that catches the light beautifully. The sheer mesh sleeves and back add a touch of allure while maintaining a sophisticated appeal. Designed to contour the body, this dress highlights your silhouette with a refined, flattering fit.
Fully bedazzled strapless bodice! Turn heads with this multi-layered skirt dress.

This captivating dress features a deep purple hue with an A-line silhouette, perfect for making a bold yet elegant statement. The delicate floral embellishments around the bodice and waist, combined with the sheer illusion neckline and back, create a romantic and refined look. The full skirt adds a playful, voluminous touch, while the intricate detailing ensures a luxurious feel. Ideal for cocktail parties or formal gatherings, this dress effortlessly balances sophistication with a touch of modern glamour.
Beautiful take on "The little black dress". Fully beaded halter style bust and form fitting skirt makes this the perfect dress for any occasion!
Stunning plum roached cocktail dress with asymmetrical design to show off your curves. The back of the dress is mostly see through mesh that connects to the beaded asymmetrical belt!
Playful taffeta dress with V-neckline showcasing a roached waist with floral accent
Showstopping little black dress! Strapless (can be converted with clip on straps)
Fully bedazzled, off shoulder, one sleeve dress! Beautiful detail on mesh sleeve to give that floating gem appearance! Two colors
Playful scoop neck chiffon dress with roached waistline to show off your curves. Two colors (burnt orange and Sangria)
Fully roached strapless cocktail dress with belted accent! Two colors (Black and Red)
Flirty strapless dress with roached bodice and multi-layered chiffon skirt. Three colors (Purple, Black, and Coral)
One shoulder Roached cocktail dress complete with floral accent satin belt. Three colors (Black, Red, Purple).

Walk like a goddess in Milano Formals E1581. A one-shoulder party dress fashioned in asymmetrical pleats of chiffon layers creating a tightly fitting bodice and well defined hipline complimenting the fitted mini-skirt. Defining the waistline is a satin waistband with floral accents and embellishment. Perfect for homecoming, date-night or junior-prom. Breathtaking fully bedazzled, strapless corset style bodice with tooled skirt.
Playful and flirty V-neck dress with multi-layered chiffon skirt. Three colors (Fushia, Navy, and Purple).

This stunning strapless cocktail dress is a captivating blend of elegance and bold design. The golden base is beautifully adorned with intricate magenta floral embroidery, creating a striking contrast that highlights the figure-flattering silhouette. The delicate detailing combined with the fitted bodice exudes sophistication and grace, making it a perfect choice for evening events, upscale parties, or special occasions. The vibrant embroidery and luxurious fabric work in harmony to make this dress a standout, offering both timeless style and modern flair.
Mermaid inspired! Strapless, sweetheart neckline with FULL sequin skirt.
Gorgeous one Shoulder, halter style dress complete with asymmetrical bodice and floral accent. The chiffon material creates a flowy and flirty feel. Three colors (Burnt orange, Royal, Charcoal).
Mermaid inspired mint hi-lo dress! The strapless corset style bodice with lace up back is completely encrusted with gems to steal the show.

This glamorous strapless dress radiates luxury with its intricate gold sequins and beaded detailing. The fitted silhouette, combined with shimmering zigzag patterns, creates a dazzling effect that accentuates the figure beautifully. The subtle sparkle of the beads, paired with the elegant gold base, makes this dress perfect for upscale events, cocktail parties, or a red-carpet appearance. Its timeless design and sophisticated embellishments make it a true show-stopper, offering both grace and boldness.

This stunning strapless teal dress combines a sleek, fitted bodice with elegant draping that flows gracefully into a knee-length skirt. The side floral detailing adds a touch of romance and charm, while the corset-style back offers both style and a tailored fit. Its shimmering fabric and refined silhouette make it an ideal choice for formal events, cocktail parties, or special occasions. The dress exudes sophistication with just the right amount of flair to make you stand out effortlessly.
Jaw-dropping cocktail dress with fully see-through back accented with floral design. The front bodice is fully bedazzled with sequins.

This sleek and sophisticated dress in a rich, deep gray tone exudes timeless elegance. The form-fitting silhouette features delicate rouching across the bodice, accentuated by a sparkling brooch at the waist that adds a touch of glamour. With its thin spaghetti straps and draped fabric, this dress flatters the figure while offering a modern and graceful look. Perfect for evening events, weddings, or formal gatherings, it combines understated luxury with refined detail.

Sweetheart strapless short dress accented with a brooch like embellishment on waist. This dress features a right hand secret pocket. Color: Coral, Pool, V-Lilac Size : 4-24 This special occasion dress is returnable. Please refer to our special occasion dress return policy (click here) for more details..
Elegant short dress with mint blue overlay and scalloped bottom.
Steal the show with the geometrically beaded bodice with cutouts to show off your waistline. The two-tone ribbon skirt makes this the ultimate party dress. Two colors (pool, pink)
This two-piece ensemble is sure to turn heads with its fully beaded halter style top and matching beaded belt sewn onto the skirt!
Vibrant multicolored dress with shallow V-neckline and stunning midriff cutout making this a playfully elegant piece.

The cropped top is sleeveless with a V-neckline and light ruching at the fitted bodice. The midriff is exposed. The coordinating skirt boasts a graphic print with a skater silhouette and modest hem.

Elegant and Romantic black and gold cocktail dress that gives you that hourglass shape.

Beautifully flowing strapless dress with multi-layered skirt. The bodice is sheer with a butterfly style detail that is perfect for that fairytale night
Feel like a princess in this deep V-neck style heavy satin dress with beaded trim. The fully beaded triple belt is sure to show off your waistline.
Cute and bubbly floral print V-neck short dress. The waist has a double beaded band with sheer fabric in between to give this dress a two-piece look!
This halter style little black dress is sure to fit any occasion with its beaded waist and peek-a-boo bust.
Turn heads with this little red dress. The plunging V-neck is offset with a sheer red mesh completing this fully beaded bodice and satin skirt.
Fairy inspired accenting covers the bust while matching teal/green mesh covers the bodice leading into a flirty chiffon skirt.
This Cinderella inspired dress has a bold sequin design on the bodice with accenting gems.
Sweet and Sophisticated! This dress has a tight fitted V-neck top with spaghetti straps and a flirty flowy skirt.
Turn heads with this little red dress. The plunging V-neck is offset with a sheer red mesh completing this fully beaded bodice and satin skirt.
This stunning red satin halter and floral dress is sure to turn heads with this innocent flirty feel.
Two piece halter style, peek-a-boo top and matching chiffon skirt. The skirt has a satin sewn on belt while the top has a lace overlay look perfect for any occasion.
Fully beaded halter style bodice with see through black mesh to give that peek-a-boo look. The skirt portion of the dress is multi-layered giving this piece a flirty feel.
Head turning strapless belted little red satin dress!

This stunning strapless dress in a delicate lilac color exudes timeless elegance. The pleated bodice adds texture and sophistication, while the black belt cinches the waist for a flattering silhouette. Its minimalist yet chic design makes it perfect for formal occasions or evening events, offering a graceful balance of modern style and classic charm.
